						               													<description>Scientists have just discovered that Amazon slug juice can give you superhuman powers!  Healthy Amazon slugs are now selling for thousands of dollars each!  You and your partner buy slug-sucking machines and head south to the Amazon to suck up as many slugs as you can sell!  The first sucker to suck up 16 slugs wins the game! &amp;#10; Decide who goes first.  Take turns scratching in the forest.  You see:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;LEAF - Good!  Slugs hide under leaves.  Scratch any space on the leaf pile to see if you find 1, 2 or 3 slugs.  Scratch this many spaces on your slug sack to mark your score.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;SLUG SLIME - Clue: there must be some slugs near this space because slugs leave a slime trail when they move.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;SNAIL - Your opponent takes 2 turns in a row because your sucked a snail by mistake and it clogged your slug-sucker.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;SQUISH - Yuck!  You stepped on a slug!  No score this turn.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;GIANT AMAZON MOTHER SLUG - Oh no!  She doesn't like you sucking up her slugs so she attacks you!  Luckily, you brought salt to defend yourself.  Throw a box of salt on your Giant Slug at the top of the card by scratching one of the 4 &amp;quot;salt boxes&amp;quot;.  You only have 4 boxes, so if you get attacked a 5th time, a Mother Slug smothers and slimes you and you lose the game!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;user summary&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
